name: Guest-1 MIK Product and 1 SDD Product and 1 MIK Class and 1 MKP with Credit Card

steps.name: Given Guest User should be on michaels home page
When user adds products with "Ship to Me, Same Day Delivery" shipping method to the cart
Then User should redirects to cart page
When the user enters frame product in the search bar
Then Click on search button to see the list of products
When User should apply filter as MarketPlace under sales and offers
When User should Click on the first marketplace product from list
When User should click on add to cart button
When User Should be click on view cart button
Then User should redirects to cart page
When User Should click on Main Menu Button
When User Click on Classes
When User Click on Online Classes
When User Click on paid checkbox
When User Select first product from list
When User Select Checkbox
When User should click on add to cart button after selecting checkoBox
When User Should be click on view cart button from class page
Then User should redirects to cart page
When User should click on checkout button
When User should select Continue As Guest button for next page
Then User should redirects to Getting Your Order page
When User should provides shipping information like Valid First Name, Last Name,Addressline1 Addressline2,city,state,zipcode,email and Phone number
When User should fill the all details of Guest one information
When User will click on payment and order review button
Then User should redirects to Payment & Order Review page
When User will add the Card Details like Name on Card,Card Number,Expiration Date,CVV
When User will click on Place order button
When User should find Order confirmation with order number
